com.interpss.core.aclf.adj
Interface PQBusLimit

All Superinterfaces:
AclfControlBus, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IAclfAdjustment, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
PQBusLimitImpl
public interface PQBusLimit
extends AclfControlBus

A representation of the model object 'PQ Bus Limit'. PQBusLimit for GenPQ bus. Object id is the same as the busId it reference to.

The following features are supported:

  • QSpecified
  • VLimit

See Also:
AclfAdjustPackage.getPQBusLimit()

hasLimitBackoff

boolean hasLimitBackoff()
Check if there is limit backoff. When (bus v = Vmax and bus q > Qspec) or (bus v = Vmin and bus q < Vspec), change the aclf bus from a PQ bus to a PV bus with bus = Vmax or Vmin.
